comments: Collins (SAS) brings his hands towards Butler (MIA) and marginal contact occurs as he releases away from the contact.
Adebayo (MIA) legally contests Vassell's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) is already in Johnson's (SAS) path and he absorbs the contact to his upper body.
Butler (MIA) brings his forearm towards Jones' (SAS) side and marginal contact occurs as he spins towards the rim.
Vassell (SAS) goes to, not through, Martin's (MIA) space and marginal contact occurs as Vassell releases away during the drive.
Adebayo (MIA) is already in Vassell's (SAS) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Lowry (MIA) and Collins (SAS) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Martin (MIA) and Johnson (SAS) briefly engage and disengage off ball.  Martin then cleanly deflects the ball away from Johnson.
Collins (SAS) legally contests Adebayo's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) brings his hand towards Jones' (SAS) side and marginal contact occurs as Jones moves down the court in transition.
Lowry (MIA) and Jones (SAS) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs as they pursue the loose ball.
Adebayo (MIA) is the last to touch the ball before is goes out of bounds.
Collins (SAS) takes an extra step forward into Lowry's (MIA) path and delivers contact during the screen.
Langford (SAS) legally contests Herro's (MIA) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Adebayo (MIA) releases away from Bassey (SAS) to secure the long rebound, and the contact is marginal.
Langford (SAS) legally contests Martin's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
Lowry (MIA) commits a take foul on Jones (SAS).
